Drive times were estimated using the python package OSMnx (Boeing, 2017). OSMnx utilizes the OpenStreetMap database to retrieve surface roads and build a graph with nodes at intersections connected by edges weighted by road distance divided by the associated speed limit. \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
